    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It requires significant mechanical repairs and bodywork to be considered roadworthy. The exterior displays extensive wear, including heavy rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with several noticeable dents and fading paint. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places, and some electronics are non-functional. The engine runs but has a noticeable knock and leaks oil. This car is best suited for someone looking for a major restoration project or for salvageable parts.",
